<text id="02-output-contract" title="pytest Project Setup — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>Output schema for the subagent applying python-pytest-setup. Encodes required boolean checks against the artefact under review.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema fragment)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ['pytest_in_pyproject', 'strict_markers', 'coverage_threshold>0', 'tests_mirror_src', 'xdist_in_ci'],
  "properties": {
    "pytest_in_pyproject": { "type": "boolean" },
    "strict_markers": { "type": "boolean" },
    "coverage_threshold>0": { "type": "boolean" },
    "tests_mirror_src": { "type": "boolean" },
    "xdist_in_ci": { "type": "boolean" }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Required fields">
    <list>
      <item>pytest_in_pyproject</item>
      <item>strict_markers</item>
      <item>coverage_threshold&gt;0</item>
      <item>tests_mirror_src</item>
      <item>xdist_in_ci</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "pytest_in_pyproject": true,
  "strict_markers": true,
  "coverage_threshold>0": true,
  "tests_mirror_src": true,
  "xdist_in_ci": true
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates green; methodology applied.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "pytest_in_pyproject": false,
  "strict_markers": false,
  "coverage_threshold>0": false,
  "tests_mirror_src": false,
  "xdist_in_ci": false
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates red; methodology not applied — fix the violations before claiming completion.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every required field is present and boolean true.</item>
      <item>Artefact references the rule id from 01-core-rules.xml (e.g., r1-pytest-only-runner).</item>
      <item>No extra properties outside the schema.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
